  "favicon": "https://static0.anpoimages.com/assets/images/favicon-240x240.51546dee.png",
  "text": "Case Material Aluminum Case size 40mm, 44mm Colors Green; Cream (40mm); Silver (44mm) Display 1.3\" AMOLED (40 mm); 1.5\" AMOLED (44 mm) CPU Samsung Exynos W1000 A fantastic smartwatch that looks good on the wrist and also delivers when it comes to features. You can now grab the Bespoke Edition for $120 off. If you're looking to buy a new smartwatch, the Samsung Galaxy Watch 7 is a great one to pick up. Not only does it look good, but it has a fantastic set of features as well. It's currently our favorite smartwatch — the best one that we think you can buy in 2025. But what makes this watch even more impressive is the steep discount that we're seeing right now, which knocks $120 off the Bespoke Edition, which drops it down to its lowest price ever at just $200. Related What's great about the Samsung Galaxy Watch 7 Bespoke Edition? Samsung's been making smartwatches for quite some time. It knows what it's doing and does it really well. The Samsung Galaxy Watch 7 is one of its best yet, delivering a sleek design that's packed with features. The Bespoke Edition is similar in hardware and software, but comes with a watchband that delivers a little more flair than the standard model. When it comes to the model that's on sale, it's the 40mm variant that features a 1.3-inch AMOLED screen that delivers colors that pop. The watch runs smoothly thanks to a Samsung Exynos W1000 chip that's paired with 2GB of RAM and 32GB of internal storage. It also features a wealth of different sensors that can track your health and fitness activities. You also get GPS tracking as well, which is great if you're in need of directions, or want to be guided on a new running path. And since this watch runs Wear OS, you're going to have access to some of the best smartwatch apps available. Furthermore, Samsung promises years of updates, which should keep this watch running stronger for longer. Overall, you won't find a better watch at this price. At $200, the Galaxy Watch 7 is an absolute steal if you're looking for something new. Just be sure to grab it from Amazon while you still can because, at this price, we don't think the deal will last long. Of course, if you want to check out some other great smartwatches, we have some excellent recommendations.",
