                  \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-on-arm-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-on-arm-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-on-arm-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-on-arm-outdoors.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                             \n                    \u003cimg width=\"12000\" height=\"6752\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Samsung Galaxy Watch 7 being worn outdoors, showing the home screen\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-on-arm-outdoors.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/samsung-galaxy-watch-7-on-arm-outdoors.jpg\"/\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-39-s-great-about-the-samsung-galaxy-watch-7-bespoke-edition\"\u003e\n                        What\u0026#39;s great about the Samsung Galaxy Watch 7 Bespoke Edition?\n               \u003c/h2\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003e Samsung\u0026#39;s been making smartwatches for quite some time. It knows what it\u0026#39;s doing and does it really well. The Samsung Galaxy Watch 7 is one of its best yet, delivering a sleek design that\u0026#39;s packed with features. The Bespoke Edition is similar in hardware and software, but comes with a watchband that delivers a little more flair than the standard model.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eWhen it comes to the model that\u0026#39;s on sale, it\u0026#39;s the 40mm variant that features a 1.3-inch AMOLED screen that delivers colors that pop. The watch runs smoothly thanks to a Samsung Exynos W1000 chip that\u0026#39;s paired with 2GB of RAM and 32GB of internal storage. It also features a wealth of different sensors that can track your health and fitness activities.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eYou also get GPS tracking as well, which is great if you\u0026#39;re in need of directions, or want to be guided on a new running path. And since this watch runs Wear OS, you\u0026#39;re going to have access to some of the best smartwatch apps available. Furthermore, Samsung promises years of updates, which should keep this watch running stronger for longer.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eOverall, you won\u0026#39;t find a better watch at this price. At $200, the Galaxy Watch 7 is an absolute steal if you\u0026#39;re looking for something new. Just be sure to grab it from Amazon while you still can because, at this price, we don\u0026#39;t think the deal will last long. Of course, if you want to check out some other great smartwatches, we have some \u003ca href=\"http://www.androidpolice.com/best-smartwatches/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eexcellent recommendations\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                                                                \n\n\n\n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
